            Requirements

            Infra
            Golang
            * param:
                define version (https://golang.org/dl/go1.16.3.linux-amd64.tar.gz)
                installation path
                platform (target Linux)
                
            * Actions
                fetch distribution file from site
                uncompress file
                move it to installation path
                add go to system path
            
            Docker (package)
                remove old version (docker docker-engine docker.io containerd runc)
                Add packages
                    Ubuntu:
                        apt-transport-https
                        ca-certificates
                        curl
                        gnupg 
                        lsb-release
                    Add gpg key (differ from Debian)
                        curl -fsSL https://download.docker.com/linux/ubuntu/gpg | sudo gpg --dearmor -o /usr/share/keyrings/docker-archive-keyring.gpg
                Setup repo
                Update
                install docker
                    can specify version
                    docker-ce=<VERSION_STRING>
                    docker-ce-cli=<VERSION_STRING>
                    containerd.io
                add user to docker group
                    which users ??
                CentOS:
                    remove packages
                    docker
                    docker-client
                    docker-client-latest
                    docker-common
                    docker-latest
                    docker-latest-logrotate
                    docker-logrotate
                    docker-engine
                    install package (fedora dnf -y install dnf-plugins-core)
                    yum-utils
                    add repo (Differ from Fedora)
                    enable repo (optional)
                    install docker
                    enable docker (service docker)
                    add user to docker

            docker-compose
            download binary from https://github.com/docker/compose/releases/download/
                ex: Bolt
                curl -L "https://github.com/docker/compose/releases/download/$PT_release/docker-compose-$(uname -s)-$(uname -m)" -o $PT_path/docker-compose
            specify version
            installation path (/usr/local/bin)
            set permissions
            

            Tools:
            howtizer
            dnammer
            flamethrower

            Metrics:
                Elatic search
                Kibana


